title: Industry by Place of Residence, Pittsburgh Pennsylvania, 2000
name: Industry by Place of Residence, Pittsburgh Pennsylvania, 2000
description: This dataset shows the number of workers in 15 categories of industry. The information is mapped according to place of residence. The data is part of the Census Transportation Planning Package (CTPP), and is the result of a cooperative effort between various groups including the State Departments of Transportation, U.S. Census Bureau, and the Federal Highway Administration. The data is a special tabulation of responses from households completing the decennial census long form. The data was collected in 2000 and is shown at tract level. This data can be found at http://www.transtats.bts.gov/Fields.asp?Table_ID=1338.
